@Meddler
• Thoughts on Aatrox in 9.3
• upcoming changes on Aatrox expectable?

Hey Meddler!{{champion:28}} 

Any plans for eve? You said she is being monitored for being too weak after the jg changes.
Any potential buffs to her? Dont think she needs more damage or lower cooldowns but she is too slow... maybe give her some base MS or while she is in stealth get more speed? Champions who do similar job simply outrun her in high and low elo as far as my experience goes.

Hello Meddler! {{champion:427}} 

Have you ever considered adding the "monster hunter experience" to Ivern's passive or making a special jungle item just for him?  Ivern players never finish the jungle item and only buy Hunter's Talisman for the experience. It also feels like such a noob trap for new Ivern players, wasting their money on a completed jungle item when they could be getting their support items earlier.

Thank you for the answer!
